Available Tools: get_page_views | get_unique_visitors | get_session_duration | get_bounce_rate
Call Schema: { "func_call": "string", "url": "string", "from_date": "string", "to_date": "string", "granularity": "hourly|daily|weekly|monthly" }
Response Schema: { "url": "string", "period": "string", "views": number, "unique_visitors": number, "avg_session_seconds": number, "bounce_rate": number }
---
Question: How many page views and unique visitors did the homepage get last week?
Call: { "func_call": "get_page_views", "url": "https://www.techcrunch.com", "from_date": "2023-10-01", "to_date": "2023-10-07", "granularity": "daily" }
Response: { "url": "https://www.techcrunch.com", "period": "2023-10-01 to 2023-10-07", "views": 452300, "unique_visitors": 189400, "avg_session_seconds": 245, "bounce_rate": 0.42 }

Question: Pull the traffic stats for our pricing page for the entire month of September.
Call: { "func_call": "get_page_views", "url": "https://shopify.com/pricing", "from_date": "2023-09-01", "to_date": "2023-09-30", "granularity": "weekly" }
Response: { "url": "https://shopify.com/pricing", "period": "2023-09-01 to 2023-09-30", "views": 89200, "unique_visitors": 67500, "avg_session_seconds": 310, "bounce_rate": 0.28 }

